### 4. `src/routes/_login/auth.ts`

**Imports:** `env` from `@/env`; `buildLoginStartPath`, `LoginOptions` from `@/lib/auth`; **`useAuthTokenSession`** from `@/server/session.server`; `redirect` from `@tanstack/react-router`; `createServerFn` from `@tanstack/react-start`.

**Pattern:** Session-backed check for `authToken`; optional bypass via `VITE_TEMP_BYPASS_AUTH`; if token present, redirects to **`/`** (not `/login`).

```7:20:/Users/duhl/git/ui/apps/org-next/src/routes/_login/auth.ts
export const redirectIfAuthenticated = createServerFn().handler(async () => {
  const session = await useAuthTokenSession();
  const hasAuthToken = !!session.data.authToken;

  if (env.VITE_TEMP_BYPASS_AUTH) {
    return;
  }

  if (hasAuthToken) {
    throw redirect({
      to: "/",
    });
  }
});
```

