### 5. `src/routes/_authed/-tenants.ts`

**Imports:** `createServerFn` from `@tanstack/react-start`; `postOrgApiJson` from `../../server/org-api.server`; Zod validator.

**Pattern:** **`createTenant`** has no session/`redirect`/`getUser` logic in the handler; it only calls `postOrgApiJson`. Token handling is centralized in `org-api.server.ts` (`useAuthTokenSession` + `getOrgApiAccessToken()`), not in this server function.

```7:29:/Users/duhl/git/ui/apps/org-next/src/routes/_authed/-tenants.ts
export const createTenant = createServerFn({ method: "POST" })
  .inputValidator(
    z.object({
      name: z.string().trim().min(1),
      tenantType: z.enum(["org", "vendor"]),
    }),
  )
  .handler(async ({ data }) => {
    try {
      return await postOrgApiJson<Tenant>("/tenants", {
        tenant: {
          name: data.name,
          tenant_type: data.tenantType as TenantType,
        },
      });
    } catch (error) {
      logServerErrorToRollbar(
        error instanceof Error ? error : new Error(String(error)),
        { serverFn: "createTenant" },
      );
      throw error;
    }
  });
```

